## 7. 工作流 JSON 格式

### 7.1 完整结构

```json
{
  "id": "workflow-{唯一标识}",
  "name": "工作流名称",
  "description": "工作流描述",
  "isActive": false,
  
  "context": {
    "projectPath": "项目路径",
    "outputPath": "输出路径",
    "assets": {
      "images": "图片目录",
      "audio": "音频目录",
      "code": "代码目录",
      "docs": "文档目录"
    }
  },
  
  "nodes": [
    // 节点列表
  ],
  
  "edges": [
    // 边列表
  ]
}
```

### 7.2 边的定义

```json
{
  "id": "edge-001",
  "source": "源节点ID",
  "target": "目标节点ID",
  "label": "边标签（可选）",
  "failCondition": {        // 可选，失败条件
    "variableName": "score",
    "operator": "lt",
    "value": 70
  }
}
```

